Roger Ashton-Griffiths https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_Ashton-Griffiths 0 Roger Ashton-Griffiths (born 19 January 1957) is an English character actor, screenwriter and film director. He is best known for his role as Mace Tyrell in HBO series Game of Thrones. Roger_Ashton-Griffiths ( born 19_January_1957 ) is an_English_character_actor , screenwriter_and_film_director .
